GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_PositioningThesis> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_PositioningThesis> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#PositioningThesis> ;
    narr:childCount "122"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "d27b99939760bb4e5400f9a43963a7c2b1a8aff1" ;
    narr:narration """The positioning of aswritten has evolved from a developer-focused tool toward a comprehensive thesis on [expertise installation](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CategoryCuratedExpertiseInstallation) as a new category of knowledge distribution. This trajectory is anchored by the [three-era framing](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TrustedInformationEra) of books, search, and now, installed human perspective. Market targeting has shifted from a developer-first enterprise model to a [B2C-primary play](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_B2CPivot), viewing solopreneurs and individuals as the volume engine, while maintaining enterprise as a high-tier use case. The product's core identity is now defined as [the memory substrate](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AswrittenIsMemorySubstrate) for steering processes, rather than an active governing loop. Recent refinements include the [CEO context-server reframe](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CEOContextServerReframe) and the [anti-monoculture amplifier](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AntiMonocultureAmplifier) thesis, which positions the platform as a tool for preserving human diversity. The go-to-market strategy has inverted from selling software adoption to [consulting-as-infrastructure](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConsultingIsMeUsingProduct), where the client receives value without ever touching the tool itself, a shift supported by the [bounded-domain fidelity argument](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_BoundedDomainFidelityArgument).""" ;
